{
  "text": "This indicates that a GenAI writing system that interacts with students needs to consider such socio-technical perspectives and demonstrate a range of explainable AI techniques and methodologies to better assist in sensemaking (Alqaraawi et al., 2020), enhancing user trust (Yang et al., 2020), or enabling shared decision making between student and AI system (Kim et al., 2024; Liao et al., 2020,)."
}